HOW TO BUILD AND RUN THE APPLICATION

There is an external GUI and a MPS project with languages


1) Building remote-gui with Maven

In a directory GUI/remote-gui run maven command:

    mvn clean package

It creates runnable JAR archive karel-gui.jar in directory GUI/remote-gui/gui/target/

Run karel-gui.jar.

2) Running project in MPS
Open project KarelG in MPS and rebuild the whole project.

In solution KarelBasic.sandbox you can run scripts or create a new one.
If karel-gui.jar is running, the script will be shown there. It is possible to run whole script or do it step by step.
If a new script from is started from MPS, previous script is discarded in karel-gui.jar and replaced with the new one.